description: If you're craving the fizzy goodness of kombucha and the serenity of tea, look no further. Eva Sippl has fused her expertise in these two types of drinks in order to brew divine one-of-a-kind concoctions at Eva's Herbucha. Portlanders in need of a delicious detox can come pour themselves the healthiest and hippest tonic to sip, straight from Eva’s tap. With a variety of carefully crafted flavors and unique herbal blends to choose from, there is a refreshingly beneficial beverage to suit your every need and to boost the best of you.
name: Eva's Herbucha
